Title: disk_utilization: scale graph metric to correct percentage value
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Component: checks
Date: 1732012675
Edition: cre
Level: 1
Version: 2.2.0p37

This werk introduces a fix to scale the graph metric 'Disk utilization'
percentage value correctly. The following check plugins are affected by
fix:

LI: diskstat_io
LI: diskstat_io_director
LI: diskstat_io_volumes
LI: aws_ebs
LI: aws_ec2_disk_io
LI: aws_rds_disk_io
LI: cadvisor_diskstat
LI: scaleio_storage_pool_totalrw
LI: scaleio_storage_pool_rebalancerw
LI: scaleio_volume
LI: ucd_diskio
LI: gcp_filestore_disk
LI: gcp_sql_disk
LI: esx_vsphere_datastore_io
